reviewText: Funny and easy on the eye...if you know what I mean

Gave this one the same consideration I did with Bikini Bandits Experience. As others have said, it's okay. A few shorts were repeated from their first movie. It's said to be all the original online clips in their g-string splender. Extras are a party for A Perfect Circle, and a trailer for Heather's Cans at Cannes. Overall it's really not that bad of a "movie," but if you've got their first one there's really no need to buy this. Rent it just for fun, but you'll probably be dissappointed. The production value and quality are still high, with excellent music and smokin' babes to keep me watching!! What made the other movie stand out versus this one are the various clips mixed within the movie. The stories were more connected and almost flowed together, where these simply were just spoonfuls of tasty cleavage.

This DVD was ok. Didn't blow my skirt up. left me feeling lonely, even depresed. Felt like eating ice cream with butterscotch. Also the the bikini's were itchy. Other then that this DVD did not have the quality I was hoping it shoud have had.

The DVD was ok, nice girls, but not enough action and booty.

I had better time watching BOOTY DOLLZ or GIRLS FROM PRAGUE, beautiful babes and nice stimulating action.....
This web series is hilarious, hot, and action packed all in one.  Don't put it past the Bikini Bandits to spice things up.  These girls are great!
